          "treatment": "NSAIDs starting day before menstruation. Heat therapy. Exercise. Rest. Alternative therapy: ginger, acupuncture."
        },
        {
          "severity": "severe_primary",
          "criteria": "severe pain, missed school/work, unresponsive to NSAIDs",
          "treatment": "COCP (continuous or cyclical). NSAIDs continued. Trial of naproxen vs ibuprofen. If still refractory, refer for pelvic exam and imaging to rule out secondary causes."
